{"_path":"/maps/_person/eratosthenes","_dir":"_person","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"埃拉托色尼","description":"求解地球周长","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"埃拉托色尼收到了良好的教育，成了一位博学的哲学家、天文学家和地理学家。他受埃及国王邀请，任皇家教师，并被任命为亚历山大里亚图书馆研究员。于 B.C. 234 接任图书馆馆长直至离世。著有《地球大小的修正》和《地理学概论》，但已遗失。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"求解地球周长"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"求解地球周长"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"塞伊尼是一个著名的景点，位于被回归线上，其中有一口井会在太阳的照射下不产生阴影。埃拉托色尼选取了和塞伊尼同经线的亚历山大的一座尖塔，并根据同一天正午的尖塔高度及其阴影长度，计算出了太阳在亚历山大的高度角。再加上他打听到的塞伊尼与亚历山大的直线距离，算出了地球的周长，约为四万公里，很接近现代测量结果。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"求解示意","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20220117233422.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Ma4y1e7rx","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"古埃及人是怎么早在2200多年前就测量出地球周长的？"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1GJ41197eB","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"伪史批判：造假的古希腊天文和地理学"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"相关"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相关"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%9F%83%E6%8B%89%E6%89%98%E8%89%B2%E5%B0%BC/464101","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"埃拉托色尼@baike"}]}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"求解地球周长","depth":2,"text":"求解地球周长"},{"id":"相关","depth":2,"text":"相关"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_person:eratosthenes.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_person/eratosthenes.md","_extension":"md"}